These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, blood-red, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes blood-red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Color   | pink | grey | blood-red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber, peach
1. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating peach##2
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Food   | peach | pineapple | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, satire, musical
1. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching musical movies##2
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | satire | horror |

 #################################

 
